        "mobile_image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/MOBILE-ImageText.jpg",
        "title": "We are sticking to our values",
        "text": "<p>Oh Polly is a brand with purpose. On seeing the awful poverty that many children were living in across southeast Asia, our founders Claire Henderson and Mike Branney started selling clothes on eBay and donating the profits to charity. After gaining huge success on eBay, Claire and Mike created their own website, but the value and purpose behind the brand was never lost.<\/p><p>Our brand is built on ethical values, and we believe we have a responsibility to help the planet, just as we're helping communities in southeast Asia. We’re performance driven and we’re committed to giving our customers unique, high-quality designs without compromising the principles that Oh Polly was built on.<\/p>",
        "desktop_horizontal_align": "desktopContentLeft",
        "mobile_horizontal_align": "mobileContentLeft",
        "desktop_vertical_align": "desktopContentCenter-y",
        "button_text": "heart of the brand",
        "button_url": "https:\/\/youtu.be\/KvvTp1tw8C8?si=d2irhCAjY_qqYM12"
      }
    },
    "1663673807c71efc0a": {
      "type": "section-image-text",
      "settings": {
        "section_margin": "spacingStandard",
        "order": "contentLeft",
        "background_colour": "{{ shop.brand.colors.primary[1].background }}",
