        "desktop_video": "",
        "desktop_image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Desktop-9.jpg",
        "mobile_video": "",
        "mobile_image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Mobile-9.jpg",
        "title": "POLLY SHARES - MONTHLY SPOTLIGHT",
        "text": "<p>We're excited to announce our 2024 Polly Placements across our London and Bromborough sites! Roles will include:<\/p><ul><li>Customer Experience<\/li><li>IT<\/li><li>Creative Pattern Cutting<\/li><li>Technical Design<\/li><\/ul><p>Here's what one of our current Industry Placements had to say about her time at Oh Polly so far:<\/p><p>\"I’ve learnt so much on my placement so far, it feels so fulfilling to be working on projects that are integral to Oh Polly’s development within the sustainability fashion space at such a critical time! Everyone has been so welcoming, and my manager has ensured I am getting the most out of my experience, I’ve had the opportunity to be involved in projects with multiple departments across the company! I am really enjoying my time at Oh Polly so far and can’t wait to see what the next year will bring!\"<br\/><strong>- India Sutherland, Sustainability Industry Placement.<\/strong><\/p>",
        "desktop_horizontal_align": "desktopContentLeft",
        "mobile_horizontal_align": "mobileContentLeft",
        "desktop_vertical_align": "desktopContentCenter-y",
        "button_text": "find out more",
        "button_url": "https:\/\/careers.ohpolly.com\/pages\/polly-placements"
      }
    },
