        "mobile_image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/MobileImage-LP_0e1a7c96-9772-4e4e-b5f9-9611cbf4d6ca_1.jpg",
        "title": "what's next for oh polly",
        "text": "<p>We know that there’s still a lot more to be done! Every year we keep getting bigger and better, which means we need to take even more responsibility for the impact of our brand. Over the next few years, we’re looking to:<\/p><ul><li>Review our packaging<\/li><li>Invest in low impact materials<\/li><li>Offer additional low impact delivery options with efficient couriers<\/li><li>Provide further information about how we produce and manufacture<\/li><li>Outline official targets for the upcoming years, with a main focus for 2030<\/li><li>Work with partners, who align with our values, to ensure we’re on track to hitting our goals<\/li><\/ul><p>We’re working hard on our official sustainability strategy and carbon reduction plan. Once we’ve completed this, we’ll update our progression, promises and targets for 2025-2050. <\/p><p>There are plenty of other exciting projects happening behind the scenes. We’ll make sure to keep everyone updated.<\/p>",
